discourse_list.title: Are these expiring ens domains owned by MakerDAO?

content.content: I came across a tweet where a user posted the following image of ens domains about to expire on 08-26-2022 wondering if they were owned by MakerDAO. There are ens domains like mkr.eth, dai.eth or maker.eth Are they owned by MakerDAO??? I hope there is someone in charge taking care of their renewal!  image1104×1179 114 KB
Hi @Marian Thanks very much for being vigilant! Most of these are owned by Dai Foundation and will be renewed.

sorenpeter:  Most of these are owned by Dai Foundation and will be renewed.   Good to know! Do we have a link to a complete list of the addresses owned by the Dai Foundation? If not, can you make a webpage (or a dedicated post) and keep it updated? thanks

Absolutely - please refer to the Asset Registry:   github.com   makerdao/asset-registry/blob/main/ENS Domains - Dai Foundation Asset Registry.md Domain Name|Status|Content Manager|Purpose|Last modification (Blank means "Grandfathered")|Delegation Target|Platform Manager (Tech Content Platform Manager)|Notes -|-|-|-|-|-|-|- dai.eth|Pre-Approved (TechOps area)|Care taker: Dai Foundation|||0x6b175474e89094c44da98b954eedeac495271d0f|TechOps for Dai Foundation| mkr.eth|Pre-Approved (TechOps area)|Care taker: Dai Foundation|||0x9f8f72aa9304c8b593d555f12ef6589cc3a579a2|TechOps for Dai Foundation| mcd.eth|N/A|N/A|||none as of yet|| dschief.mcd.eth|Pre-Approved (TechOps area)|Care taker: Dai Foundation|||0x0....|TechOps for Dai Foundation| dspause.mcd.eth|Pre-Approved (TechOps area)|Care taker: Dai Foundation|||0x0....|TechOps for Dai Foundation| medianizer.eth|Pre-Approved (TechOps area)|Care taker: Dai Foundation|||0x0....|TechOps for Dai Foundation| maker.eth|N/A|N/A|||none as of yet|| vote.maker.eth|Pre-Approved|DUX|||none as of yet|TechOps for DUX|https://gateway.ipfs.com/<ipfs-hash> auctions.maker.eth|Pre-Approved|SideStream CU / SES CU|||none as of yet|TechOps for SideStream CU / SES CU|https://gateway.ipfs.com/<ipfs-hash> scaling.maker.eth|Pre-Approved|SES CU|||none as of yet|TechOps for SES CU|https://gateway.ipfs.com/<ipfs-hash>       ---        This file has been truncated. show original
Good to know that they are taking care of these renewals. Thank for your answer.

I’m a little jealous because this information was shared by me earlier and it went unnoticed     Recopilación de Noticias sobre MakerDAO, DAI y MKR   Esto podría ser de interés para el DAO. https://twitter.com/etheraltog/status/1562408208160940032
